<title>FAIRER THAN THE MORNING</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zing khawvak sang in Na hawih zaw'i,
 Aw, ei Hukdampa, Lalpen;
 Na lopi, lalzie la a sak,
 Ka lungthim a kipak hi.

[V2]
 Zing khawvak sangin Na hawih zaw'i,
 Na vakzaw'i sun laitak sang inle;
 Na umna mun lopi achun,
 Thimna leh dahna umlo.

[V3]
 2. Vakna'n puon banga kizem in,
 Lal lopina lukhuk khu'n;
 Lalgam a thuneihna chengcheng,
 Kumsawt in Nanga ahi.

[V4]
 3. Aw, Na hehpihna lopina,
 Na zahngaihna lopi tawh;
 Na hehpihna chun Lalgam ah,
 Kei di'n mun ei bawlsak hi.

[V5]
 4. Ka khawvel hun hih a beih tieng,
 Leisiet hinkhuo a beih tieng;
 Amuna-mun sang tamzaw tawh,
 Kumsawt in la sa ta'ng kau.</lyrics>
</song>